==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skelter
<hw>Skel"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Helter-skelter</er>.]</ety> <def>To run off helter-skelter; to
hurry; to scurry; -- with <xex>away</xex> or <xex>off</xex>.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark> <rj><au>A. R. Wallace.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

